column2: #You only need to run this ONCE to draw from the same Qualtrics account.
#If you change Qualtrics accounts you will need to get a different token.
Your original .Renviron will be backed up and stored in your R HOME directory if needed.

Your Qualtrics key and base URL have been stored in your .Renviron.  
To use now, restart R or run `readRenviron("~/.Renviron")`
